<!--Views/Home/Privacy-->
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
                    <p>Welcome to WellUp's Privacy Policy. This document explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website and water delivery services.</p>
                    <p>At WellUp, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your personal information is handled securely and responsibly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
                    <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>

                    <h5>Personal Information:</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Name, email address, and phone number</li>
                        <li>Delivery address details</li>
                        <li>Account login credentials (encrypted)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5>Usage Information:</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Order history and preferences</li>
                        <li>Website usage and interaction data</li>
                        <li>IP address and browser information</li>
                        <li>Device information</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                    <p>We use your information to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Process and deliver your orders</li>
                        <li>Create and manage your customer account</li>
                        <li>Communicate with you about your orders and services</li>
                        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
                        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>4. Data Security</h3>
                    <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. These measures include:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Encryption of sensitive data</li>
                        <li>Secure user authentication</li>
                        <li>Regular security assessments</li>
                        <li>Limited access to personal information by our employees</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>5. Data Sharing</h3>
                    <p>We may share your information with:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Delivery partners to fulfill your orders</li>
                        <li>Service providers who help us operate our business</li>
                        <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
                    <p>You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access your personal information</li>
                        <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
                        <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
                        <li>Object to certain processing of your data</li>
                        <li>Download a copy of your data</li>
                        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>7. Changes to This Policy</h3>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date below.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>8. Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Facebook Page: Well up Water Industries </li>
                        <li>Phone: +63 917 508 1619</li>
                        <li>4HVW+J4W, D Fajardo St, Angeles, Pampanga</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                <p>Last Updated: May 15, 2025</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>